highlights.text: Yaanji - From "Vikram Vedha" by Sam C.S., Anirudh Ravichander, and Shakthisree Gopalan has been on Top Songs Chennai the longest, at 66 weeks straight.
Jolly O Gymkhana (From "Beast") by Thalapathy Vijay and Anirudh Ravichander is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Chennai, up 28 spots at #71.
Anirudh Ravichander has the most spots on Top Songs Chennai. Jimikki Ponnu is the highest at #4.
Oru Paadhi Kadhavu by Thushani Pillai and Jerone B is the highest new entry on Top Songs Chennai at #54.
